### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

### Nearby stations
GET http://localhost:8000/api/stations/nearby?lat=51.45&lng=6.76&radius_km=10&fuel_type=e10&sort=price

### Sync nearby
POST http://localhost:8000/api/stations/sync-nearby
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lat": 51.45,
  "lng": 6.76,
  "radius_km": 10,
  "fuel_type": "e10",
  "sort": "price"
}

### Current prices
GET http://localhost:8000/api/prices/current?station_ids=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

